<scriptment id="82000" point="caps_time" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-11-01" status="final">
	<part>
		<condition>
			<comment>The Player hired Capucine Rousseau.</comment>
			<narration>Soleil passes the Cardboard City. Capucine sits on a cardboard box and stares at her watch.</narration>
			<line id="1000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Wow, 5:31 PM and you aren't asleep?</line>
			<line id="2000" speaker="capucine" voicelang="fr">Right now?</line>
			<line id="3000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Right now.</line>
			<line id="4000" speaker="capucine" voicelang="fr">Too soon!</line>
			<narration>Capucine yawns.</narration>
			<line id="5000" speaker="capucine" voicelang="ja">Can't sleep.</narration>
			<line id="6000" speaker="capucine" voicelang="ja">No time.</narration>
			<narration>Capucine tosses the watch. She marches back towards Sega Headquarters.</narration>
			<line id="7000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Godspeed.</narration>
			<comment>Capucine's Base Ambition reaches 90%.</comment>
		</condition>
	</part>
</scriptment>